## "encoding" model
| Property | Definition | Value type | Repeatable |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| value | String describing the encoding. | String | No |
| code | Code representing the encoding. | String | No |
| uri | URI for the encoding. | String | No |
| note | Other information related to the encoding. Note types must be from the "note" controlled list. | Object ("description" model) | Yes |
| source | The vocabulary, authority, or other origin for the encoding. | Object ("source" model) | No |
| version | The version of the encoding. | String | No |
